docker setup
------------




permission problem when newly created user try to using docker
--------------------------------------------------------------
$(cloud_server) uname -a
Linux cloud-server-1 4.15.0-74-generic #84-Ubuntu SMP Thu Dec 19 08:06:2

# try using docker cmd as user: metung -> failed
$(cloud_server) docker ps
Got permission denied while trying to connect to the Docker daemon sockeontainers/json": dial unix /var/run/docker.sock: connect: permission den

# using docker cmd as root -> succeed
$(cloud_server) sudo docker ps
CONTAINER ID   IMAGE     COMMAND   CREATED   STATUS    PORTS     NAMES

# add metung into docker group
$(cloud_server) sudo usermod -a -G docker metung

# but sill failed to use docker cmd
$(cloud_server) docker ps
Got permission denied while trying to connect to the Docker daemon sockeontainers/json": dial unix /var/run/docker.sock: connect: permission den

# create a new ssh connection && test docker cmd -> succeed
metung@cloud-server-1:~$ docker ps
CONTAINER ID   IMAGE     COMMAND   CREATED   STATUS    PORTS     NAMES

